headline.main: Judge: Dad Who Dropped Girl Off Bridge Ready to Stand Trial
headline.print_headline: Judge: Dad Who Dropped Girl Off Bridge Ready to Stand Trial

lead_paragraph: Two people were killed after fire broke out at a camp housing hundreds of migrants who pick fruit and vegetables in the fields of southern Italy, officials said.
